            <h2 id="ds_byfax" class="size-20">My Agency Has No Deaths to Report. Do I Have to Fill Anything Out?</h2>
            <p>Yes. If your agency has no deaths to report, you need to submit only the DCRA Annual Summary (CJ-13). Completing this form will take about 5 minutes. The information collected is necessary to calculate a true count of all deaths as defined by the DCRA of 2013.</p>
