            <h2 id="abt_asj" class="size-20">How do I report data to the DCRA Collection Program?</h2>
            <p>Data may be entered directly into the online forms, which are available through the DCRA website, <a href="www.doj-dcra.org">www.doj-dcra.org</a>.</p>
            <p>All access to the reporting section of the DCRA Collection Program website requires a secure login and password. Each federal law enforcement agency will receive instructions to log into the system. If you are having difficulty accessing the system or have not received your login information, please call the DCRA Collection Program Helpdesk at (877) 262-7654 or send an e-mail to <a href="mailto:doj-dcra@rti.org">doj-dcra@rti.org</a>.</p>
